</inline-formula>。</p><p>证：<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x74_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>类似的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x75_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>方向也有相同的结论。</p><p>引理2 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19461-ref12">12</xref>] ：设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x76_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上的网格函数，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x78_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>引理3 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19461-ref12">12</xref>] ：对于时间序列<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x79_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，任意的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。有：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19461-formula29"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x82_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>引理4 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19461-ref12">12</xref>] ：假设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x83_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是一个非负序列，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x84_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，并且非负序列<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250485x85_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>满足</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.